{{Rosary}}
'''''The Power of the Rosary''''' is a book on [[Catholic]] themes by Reverend Albert J. M. Shamon.

The book revolves around the topic of [[Catholic beliefs on the power of prayer]] via the [[rosary]]. It builds on the [[fifteen rosary promises]] and extends the discussion to the present day. It discusses that the rosary has been featured prominently in the context of several [[Marian apparition]]s such as those in [[Međugorje]] and [[Our Lady of Fatima]]. It also recounts many anecdotal incidents regarding the rosary, ranging from religious and political prisoners in China to every day Catholics.

